{"id":23138,"date":"2022-12-20T08:58:27","date_gmt":"2022-12-20T07:58:27","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/?page_id=23138"},"modified":"2023-10-09T12:46:07","modified_gmt":"2023-10-09T10:46:07","slug":"msa-wellness","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/karriar\/att-arbeta-hos-oss\/msa-wellness\/","title":{"rendered":"MSA Wellness"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"preamble\">V\u00e5ra medarbetare \u00e4r byr\u00e5ns absolut viktigaste tillg\u00e5ng och vi \u00e4r d\u00e4rf\u00f6r m\u00e5na om att tilltala, utveckla och beh\u00e5lla de b\u00e4sta talangerna. F\u00f6r oss \u00e4r det av st\u00f6rsta vikt att v\u00e5ra medarbetare trivs och m\u00e5r bra.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-23644 alignnone\" src=\"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/03\/msa-wellness.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"827\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/03\/msa-wellness.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/03\/msa-wellness-800x551.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/03\/msa-wellness-768x529.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Fysiskt och psykiskt v\u00e4lbefinnande h\u00e4nger ofta ihop, under 2022 lanserade vi d\u00e4rf\u00f6r MSA Wellness som \u00e4r byr\u00e5ns koncept f\u00f6r att uppmuntra till tr\u00e4ning tillsammans. Vi erbjuder \u00e5terkommande fysiska aktiviteter samt f\u00f6rel\u00e4sningar, t\u00e4vlingar och m\u00f6jligheter att prova p\u00e5 nya tr\u00e4ningsformer. Allt f\u00f6r att inspirera till en mer h\u00e4lsosam vardag och fr\u00e4mja v\u00e4lm\u00e5ende och fysisk aktivitet b\u00e5de p\u00e5 och utanf\u00f6r arbetet.<\/p>\n<h2>Ett urval av aktiviteter<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Grupptr\u00e4ning p\u00e5 gym<\/li>\n<li>Fotboll<\/li>\n<li>L\u00f6pning<\/li>\n<li>Innebandy<\/li>\n<li>Yoga<\/li>\n<li>Kl\u00e4ttring<\/li>\n<li>F\u00f6rel\u00e4sningar<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Under 2023 utvecklade vi konceptet ytterligare och lanserade MSA Wellness Day, en \u00e5rligen \u00e5terkommande dag d\u00e5 byr\u00e5n erbjuder alla medarbetare ledighet och tid f\u00f6r \u00e5terh\u00e4mtning.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>V\u00e5ra medarbetare \u00e4r byr\u00e5ns absolut viktigaste tillg\u00e5ng och vi \u00e4r d\u00e4rf\u00f6r m\u00e5na om att tilltala, utveckla och beh\u00e5lla de b\u00e4sta talangerna. F\u00f6r oss \u00e4r det\u2026<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":0,"parent":8780,"menu_order":4,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-23138","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"acf":[],"lang":"sv","translations":{"sv":23138,"en":23638},"pll_sync_post":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/23138"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/4"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=23138"}],"version-history":[{"count":14,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/23138\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":25815,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/23138\/revisions\/25815"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/8780"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=23138"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}